16 February 2012Members of the media are invited to the post State of the Nation Address (SoNA) media briefing of the Human Development Cluster. The Chairperson of the cluster, Minister of Basic Education, Angie Motshekga will lead the briefing.The details are as follows: Date: Friday, 17 February 2012 Time: 10h00 Venue: Imbizo Media Centre in Parliament, Cape TownNB: There will be a video-link to GCIS Auditorium, 1st Floor, Midtown Building, PretoriaMinisters from the following departments will attend the briefing:Kindly confirm attendance by email or sms to: Professor Ndawonde (Pretoria) E-mail: proffesor@gcis.gov.za Cell: 078 456 5738Mzimasi Ngqelu (Cape Town) E-mail: mzi@gcis.gov.za Cell: 076 904 3557Enquiries: Pheliswa Sebati (Pretoria) Cell: 082 413 4609Liezil Cerf (Cape Town) Cell: 076 778 2380